EcoWPCDeck are innovative products, made from recycled materials (wood, plastic) and are 100% recycable.  Being made as combination of the mentioned materials, they incorporate the good sides of both items  - the natural look and emphasized relief structure of wood and the practicality of plastic, while respecting, today much needed, renewability.

They find application in the exterior, making terraces, facades, benches, fences, etc. much more practical, durable and unsurpassed in terms of design.

They are made by extrusion (standard decking) and co-extrusion (ASA products) as decking, facades, fences and benches, and have warranty of 5 and 10 years, respectively.

Why to choose EcoWPCDeck as a business partner?
- the only decking manufacturer in the region, with confirmed high-level production technology, extrusion and co-extrusion;
- possibility of production according to special orders (pattern, length);
- the target group are associates-installers, with who we contract special conditions of purchase and offer benefits, namely:
          - business without warehouse/stocks – goods from the manufacturer's warehouse can go directly to the construction site;
          - wide range of products and designs;
          - possibility of special orders;
          - the possibility of monitoring the manufacturer with assembly, when it comes to sales to end customers;
          - the manufacturer takes responsibility for product quality;
          - an expert team that manages production with decades of international experience in the field of PVC floors.

Address: Ive Lole Ribara 294, 21400 Bačka Palanka, Serbia
Telephone: +381 (67) 716 23 23

Comercializamos materiais elétricos de qualidade, proporcionando aos clientes soluções sustentáveis em Automação Industrial, Iluminação e Instalações Elétricas.

Temos equipe de engenheiro e eletrotécnicos com experiência em soluções industriais.

Somos revenda autorizada e integrador WEG desde 2010. WEG líder no segmento de motores, drives e controls no Brasil.

Somos montadores de painéis, quadros elétricos e chaves especiais sob medida, dedicados para aplicações seriadas, como fabricantes de máquinas, revendas, etc, tais como:

Quadros para bancadas didáticas;

